data-triple-N3.o: "The Cannes International Film Festival, is an annual film festival held in Cannes, France, which previews new films of all genres, including documentaries, from around the world. Founded in 1946, it is one of the most prestigious and publicized film festivals in the world. The invitation-only festival is held annually (usually in May) at the Palais des Festivals et des Congres. The 2012 Cannes Film Festival took place from May 16 to May 27, 2012."@en
